herapeutics</a></h2><p><strong>FounderDNA:</strong> Serial Founder, Technical Founder, Doctorate Degree, Prior Exit</p><p><strong>Prior Experience:</strong> CEO, Board Chair &amp; Co-Founder, Gallop Oncology at PureTech Health, Director, Board of Directors at Abcam, Founder &amp; Managing Partner, Binney Street Capital Venture Fund at Dana-Farber Cancer Institute</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/lubagreenwood\">LinkedIn</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.mwyngil.com/\">Mwyngil Therapeutics</a> is a biopharmaceutical company developing first-in-class and best-in-class small-molecule therapies for cardiovascular, metabolic, and chronic inflammatory and immune diseases.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> Boston, Massachusetts, United States</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Biotechnology, Pharmaceuticals</p><div><hr></div><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.agentcard.sh/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Qw1q!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F85fae4ca-8ecd-4cca-ab6b-7ea80e2f423c_1386x756.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Qw1q!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F85fae4ca-8ecd-4cca-ab6b-7ea80e2f423c_1386x756.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Qw1q!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F85fae4ca-8ecd-4cca-ab6b-7ea80e2f423c_1386x756.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Qw1q!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F85fae4ca-8ecd-4cca-ab6b-7ea