ttps://www.stay-nimble.com/\">The Nimble Company</a> is building an intelligence layer that connects what you already know and surfaces missed insights at the right moment, aiming to compound scattered information into sharper instincts and faster decisions rather than requiring manual filing and searching.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> London Area, United Kingdom</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Personal Knowledge Management, Artificial Intelligence | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 2</p><div><hr></div><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Company Launch Tracker&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\"><span>Share Company Launch Tracker</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p>Stay strapped in,</p><p>Drake</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Thanks for reading. If you enjoyed this, share it with your friends, colleagues, and anyone who wants to stay ahead of the latest startup launches and emerging companies in tech.</em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Company Launch Tracker #89]]></title><description><![CDATA[Stanford MBA builds AI ops layer for consumer brands, Ex-JPMorgan & Apple AI lead builds on-premise AI hardware for hospitals, & Ex-AWS researcher builds formal verification for AI-generated co