9 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><em><strong><a href=\"http://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/\">Company Launch Tracker</a></strong> is a real-time feed for investors, founders, and tech enthusiasts who want to spot startups the moment they launch. We leverage the technology built at <strong><a href=\"https://launchgravity.com/\">Gravity</a></strong> to track billions of data points and surface company debuts the instant they happen. These signals include founder &#8220;I&#8217;m excited to announce&#8230;&#8221; posts, company filings, job changes, product hunt launches, and early press mentions&#8212;all stitched together into a single stream of what&#8217;s new.</em></p><div><hr></div><p>In this issue of the Company Launch Tracker, here is what we will uncover:</p><ul><li><p>Bridgewater and BlackRock alum is building a compliance operations platform for manufacturers</p></li><li><p>Former Discord machine learning engineer is building infrastructure for scaling autoresearch, backed by YC S26</p></li><li><p>Former Zendesk GTM director and SAP executive is building a decision intelligence platform for security teams</p></li><li><p>Ex-Google conversational AI architect is building enterprise AI solutions for maritime organizations</p></li><li><p>And more&#8230;</p></li></ul><p>Here&#8217;s the rundown of new company activity&#8230; &#128640;&#128640;&#128640;</p><div><hr></div><h1>&#128640;Recent Company Launches</h1><blockquote><p><em>Early visibility into the launches most people won&#8217;t hear about until months later.</em></p></blockquote><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.katalyzeai.com/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!79Er!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7d2aee1-2c2a-49c1-96fe-e0f0a3900ebe_1266x652.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!79Er!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7d2aee1-2c2a-49c1-96fe-e0f0a3900ebe_1266x652.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!79Er!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7d2aee1-2c2a-49c1-96fe-e0f0a3900ebe_1266x652.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!79Er!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7d2aee1-2c2a-49c1-96fe-e0f0a3900ebe_1266x652.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!79Er!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7d2aee1-2c2a-49c1-96fe-e0f0a3900ebe_1266x652.png\" width=\"1266\" height=\"652\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&q