acker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Company Launch Tracker&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\"><span>Share Company Launch Tracker</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p>Stay strapped in,</p><p>Drake</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Thanks for reading. If you enjoyed this, share it with your friends, colleagues, and anyone who wants to stay ahead of the latest startup launches and emerging companies in tech.</em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Company Launch Tracker #86]]></title><description><![CDATA[Ex-Talabat CEO & Uber veteran builds driverless delivery networks, Ex-Wells Fargo SVP reimagines CRE underwriting with AI, & Ex-HubSpot engineer builds infra for accurate, explainable AI search]]></description><link>https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/p/company-launch-tracker-86</link><guid isPermaLink=\"false\">https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/p/company-launch-tracker-86</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Drake Dukes]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 18:01:18 GMT</pubDate><enclosure url=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png\" length=\"0\" type=\"image/jpeg\"/><content:encoded><![CDATA[<div