drive the test loop, without building the custom test infrastructure that typically takes a team a year to assemble.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> San Francisco, California, United States / Australia</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Developer Tools, Hardware Test &amp; Validation, Artificial Intelligence | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 3</p><div><hr></div><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://theblanket.ai/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!fsm6!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9be18020-62e2-42fb-ac02-4f2355307eec_1342x664.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!fsm6!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9be18020-62e2-42fb-ac02-4f2355307eec_1342x664.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!fsm6!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9be18020-62e2-42fb-ac02-4f2355307eec_1342x664.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!fsm6!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9be18020-62e2-42fb-ac02-4f2355307eec_1342x664.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!fsm6!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9be18020-62e2-42fb-ac02-4f2355307eec_1342x664.png\" width=\"1342\" height=\"664\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9be18020-62e2-42fb-ac02-4f2355307eec_1342x664.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscre