ctrolysis that improves the energy efficiency, cost, and durability of green hydrogen production.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> Germany</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Green Hydrogen, Deep Tech/Cleantech | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 5</p><p><strong>Latest Funding:</strong> The company is backed by EUR 1.4 million in public funding and supported by advisors from the Max Planck Institute for Chemical Energy Conversion.</p><div><hr></div><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://revyl.com/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CUi2!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f80ae2c-4b34-4cf6-af84-a83d89700279_1382x704.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CUi2!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f80ae2c-4b34-4cf6-af84-a83d89700279_1382x704.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CUi2!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f80ae2c-4b34-4cf6-af84-a83d89700279_1382x704.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CUi2!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f80ae2c-4b34-4cf6-af84-a83d89700279_1382x704.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CUi2!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f80ae2c-4b34-4cf6-af84-a83d89700279_1382x704.png\" width=\"1382\" height=\"704\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9f80ae2c-4b34-4cf6-af