=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2>Marianna Anastasakou - Founder &amp; CEO at <a href=\"https://www.axocare.health/\">Axocare Health</a></h2><p><strong>FounderDNA:</strong> Serial Founder, Masters Degree, Top 10 University</p><p><strong>Prior Experience:</strong> Co-Founder at RespiGene, Global Director of Strategy at Verma Drugs, Business Unit Director at Pharmathen, Oncology Product Manager at AstraZeneca</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/marianna-anastasakou\">LinkedIn</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.axocare.health/\">Axocare Health</a> is a clinically validated digital platform providing structured, evidence-based support tools to family caregivers of patients with Parkinson&#8217;s disease and dementia.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> Greece</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Digital Health, Neurology</p><div><hr></div><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Company Launch Tracker&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\"><span>Share Company Launch Tracker</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p>Stay strapped in,</p><p>Drake</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Thanks for reading. If you enjoyed this, share it with your friends, colleagues, and anyone who wants to stay ahead of the latest startup launches and emerging companies in tech.</em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-