 AI research lab</p></li><li><p>KTH Royal Institute of Technology spinout builds enterprise automation with mathematically guaranteed AI</p></li><li><p>AWS and Lab126 tech lead is building AI teammates for industrial maintenance operations</p></li><li><p>Ex-Ripple and CME Group alum is building an AI tool for closer human relationships</p></li><li><p>And more&#8230;</p></li></ul><p>Here&#8217;s the rundown of new company activity&#8230; &#128640;&#128640;&#128640;</p><div><hr></div><h1>&#128640;Recent Company Launches</h1><blockquote><p><em>Early visibility into the launches most people won&#8217;t hear about until months later.</em></p></blockquote><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.coreauto.com/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4yCo!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9dcc6a10-3eed-4b4b-b647-05a0e7a8a107_3456x1866.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4yCo!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9dcc6a10-3eed-4b4b-b647-05a0e7a8a107_3456x1866.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4yCo!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9dcc6a10-3eed-4b4b-b647-05a0e7a8a107_3456x1866.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4yCo!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9dcc6a10-3eed-4b4b-b647-05a0e7a8a107_3456x1866.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4yCo!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.a