tructure &amp; Platform Engineer at DeepL, Research Intern at Microsoft</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/simon-campion-96170a1bb\">LinkedIn</a></p><p><a href=\"https://heplon.com/\">Heplon</a> is a natural language layer that integrates with existing platforms to make them progressively easier to use over time.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> Bonn, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Artificial Intelligence, Developer Tools | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 2</p><div><hr></div><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Company Launch Tracker&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\"><span>Share Company Launch Tracker</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p>Stay strapped in,</p><p>Drake</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Thanks for reading. If you enjoyed this, share it with your friends, colleagues, and anyone who wants to stay ahead of the latest startup launches and emerging companies in tech.</em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Company Launch Tracker #77]]></title><description><![CDATA[Ex-Neuralink & Tesla engineer builds automated QA for firmware teams, Stanford MBA builds AI compliance automation for Medicaid behavioral health, & Harvard alum builds IDE for robotics teams]]></description><link>https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/p/company-launch-tracker-77</link><guid isPermaLink=\"false\">https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/p/company-launch-tracker-77</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Drake Dukes]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 17:01:49 GMT</pubDate><enclosure url=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png\" length=\"0\" type=\"image/jpeg\"/><content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src