</span></a></p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Company Launch Tracker #76]]></title><description><![CDATA[Tesla alum builds robotic pitstops for autonomous fleets, Clearbit co-founder builds a data-cleaning layer for Procore, & Ex-Amazon ML engineer builds an AI company brain for engineering teams]]></description><link>https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/p/company-launch-tracker-76</link><guid isPermaLink=\"false\">https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/p/company-launch-tracker-76</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Drake Dukes]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 18:01:14 GMT</pubDate><enclosure url=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png\" length=\"0\" type=\"image/jpeg\"/><content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c