ch. We leverage the technology built at <strong><a href=\"https://launchgravity.com/\">Gravity</a></strong> to track billions of data points and surface company debuts the instant they happen. These signals include founder &#8220;I&#8217;m excited to announce&#8230;&#8221; posts, company filings, job changes, product hunt launches, and early press mentions&#8212;all stitched together into a single stream of what&#8217;s new.</em></p><div><hr></div><p>In this issue of the Company Launch Tracker, here is what we will uncover:</p><ul><li><p>Ex-Tesla engineer and founder of Pushme (acquired by TIER Mobility) launches robotic pitstops for autonomous vehicle fleets</p></li><li><p>Co-founder of Clearbit (acquired by HubSpot) building a spreadsheet layer on Procore to clean and sync messy construction data</p></li><li><p>Ex-Palantir and Amazon ML engineer building a company brain for engineering teams</p></li><li><p>Co-creator of CryptoKitties and VP of Product at Dapper Labs launches semi-stealth startup</p></li><li><p>And more&#8230;</p></li></ul><p>Here&#8217;s the rundown of new company activity&#8230; &#128640;&#128640;&#128640;</p><div><hr></div><h1>&#128640;Recent Company Launches</h1><blockquote><p><em>Early visibility into the launches most people won&#8217;t hear about until months later.</em></p></blockquote><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.aseonlabs.com/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!r0N0!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb9246aea-adde-4b4c-b4c6-b1fd97734bca_1387x780.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!r0N0!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb9246aea-