A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb9246aea-adde-4b4c-b4c6-b1fd97734bca_1387x780.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!r0N0!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb9246aea-adde-4b4c-b4c6-b1fd97734bca_1387x780.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!r0N0!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb9246aea-adde-4b4c-b4c6-b1fd97734bca_1387x780.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2>George Kalligeros - Co-Founder &amp; CEO at <a href=\"https://www.aseonlabs.com/\">Aseon Labs</a></h2><p><strong>FounderDNA:</strong> Serial Founder, Technical Founder, Masters Degree, Prior Exit</p><p><strong>Prior Experience:</strong> Co-Founder &amp; CEO at Pushme (acquired by TIER Mobility), VP Commercial &amp; Strategy at Dragonfly, VP Hardware at TIER Mobility, Mechanical Design Engineer at Tesla</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kalligeros\">LinkedIn</a> or <a href=\"mailto:george@aseonlabs.com\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.aseonlabs.com/\">Aseon Labs</a> builds robotic pitstops for autonomous vehicle fleets. A depot-in-a-box systems for charging, cleaning, and inspecting self-driving cars directly in operating zones.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> Redwood City, California, United States</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Robotics, Autonomous Vehicles, Fleet Infrastructure | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 2</p><div><hr></div><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sandspit.app/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FLWE!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fac323dd3-1267-493f-b44f-1843431e02eb_1391x780.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FLWE!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fac323dd3-1267-493f-b44f-1843431e02eb_1391x780.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FLWE!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fac323dd3-1267-493f-b44f-1843431e02eb_1391x780.png 1272w, htt