mp; CTO at Clearbit (acquired by HubSpot), Principal Engineer at HubSpot, Platform Architect at HotelTonight (acquired by Airbnb), VP Engineering at Bills.com</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/harlow-ward\">LinkedIn</a> or <a href=\"mailto:harlow@sandspit.app\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.sandspit.app/\">Sandspit</a> is a spreadsheet layer on top of Procore that turns messy construction inputs &#8212; T&amp;M invoices, submittals, RFIs, and spreadsheets &#8212; into a reviewable, bulk-editable grid, catching bad data early and syncing clean records back to Procore.</p><p><strong>HQ: </strong>Santa Barbara, California, United States</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> ConTech, Construction Software, B2B SaaS</p><div><hr></div><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://chipper.bio/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!KfCj!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29ecc8f4-9b11-4bbd-b7f1-f0685a27b139_1384x774.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!KfCj!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29ecc8f4-9b11-4bbd-b7f1-f0685a27b139_1384x774.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!KfCj!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29ecc8f4-9b11-4bbd-b7f1-f0685a27b139_1384x774.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!KfCj!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F29ecc8f4-9b11-4bbd-b7f1-f0685a27b139_1384x774.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/i