tride.world/\">Stride World</a></h2><p><strong>FounderDNA:</strong> Serial Founder, Technical Founder, Former FAANG</p><p><strong>Prior Experience:</strong> Senior Product Development &amp; GTM Lead at Meta, VP Product Management at Trustpilot, Founder at JayCee Chocolates, Product Partnerships Lead at blinkbox</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/jcheseldine\">LinkedIn</a> or <a href=\"mailto:james@stride.world\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"https://stride.world/\">Stride World</a> continuously benchmarks CRM data against a validated market view, using AI agents to surface missing, wrong, or outdated records most likely to affect routing, segmentation, pricing, and pipeline quality &#8212; then syncs recommended fixes into existing GTM systems.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> London Area, United Kingdom</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Sales Intelligence, CRM Data, Revenue Operations | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 2</p><div><hr></div><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Company Launch Tracker&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\"><span>Share Company Launch Tracker</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p>Stay strapped in,</p><p>Drake</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Thanks for reading. If you enjoyed this, share it with your friends, colleagues, and anyone who wants to stay ahead of the latest startup launches and emerging companies in tech.</em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:nul