0\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2>Matt Zaheen - Co-Founder at <a href=\"https://tynapse.com/en\">Tynapse</a></h2><p><strong>FounderDNA:</strong> Serial Founder, Technical Founder, Masters Degree, Former FAANG</p><p><strong>Prior Experience:</strong> Head of Marketing at Zoom, Head of Consumer &amp; Partnerships Marketing at Meta, Director &amp; Head of Marketing at Google APAC, Founder &amp; CEO at 1yes</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mattzaheen\">LinkedIn</a> or <a href=\"mailto:matt@tynapse.com\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"https://tynapse.com/en\">Tynapse</a> is building a trust layer for enterprise AI, enabling organizations to deploy AI systems with greater security, reliability, and governance.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> South Korea</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> Enterprise AI, Trust &amp; Safety | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 7</p><div><hr></div><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Company Launch Tracker&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\"><span>Share Company Launch Tracker</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p>Stay strapped in,</p><p>Drake</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Thanks for reading. If you enjoyed this, share it with your friends, colleagues, and anyone who wants to stay ahead of the latest startup launches and emerging companies in tech.</em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-componen