etch/$s_!gnRR!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gnRR!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F286984fd-7c8d-417c-9127-3f1add72c010_1442x887.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><em><strong><a href=\"http://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/\">Company Launch Tracker</a></strong> is a real-time feed for investors, founders, and tech enthusiasts who want to spot startups the moment they launch. We leverage the technology built at <strong><a href=\"https://launchgravity.com/\">Gravity</a></strong> to track billions of data points and surface company debuts the instant they happen. These signals include founder &#8220;I&#8217;m excited to announce&#8230;&#8221; posts, company filings, job changes, product hunt launches, and early press mentions&#8212;all stitched together into a single stream of what&#8217;s new.</em></p><div><hr></div><p>In this issue of the Company Launch Tracker, here is what we will uncover:</p><ul><li><p>Repeat founder who sold Forethought to Zendesk is building an AI-native personal productivity assistant</p></li><li><p>Ex-Waymo, Aurora, and Uber Self-Driving PM builds the real-time Physical AI intelligence layer for autonomous port and maritime operations</p></li><li><p>Ex-DuPont senior scientist is developing bio-based rubber alternatives from European forestry waste</p></li><li><p>Ex-Square Capital and Bond CTO launches an open, agentic-AI-native alternative to Google and Apple Photos</p></li><li><p>And more&#8230;</p></li></ul><p>Here&#8217;s the rundown of new company activity&#8230; &#128640;&#128640;&#128640;</p><div><hr></div><h1>&#128640;Recent Company Launches</h1><blockquote><p><em>Early visibility into the launches most people won&#8217;t hear about until months later.</em></p></blockquote><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://espa.ai/\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!6Fqs!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf44742-3d30-4cad-80a1-5a71041d9cf3_1330x745.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/imag