V. - CEO &amp; Co-Founder at <a href=\"https://rubra-q.com/\">Greewave</a></h2><p><strong>FounderDNA:</strong> Technical Founder, Doctorate Degree, Masters Degree</p><p><strong>Prior Experience:</strong> PhD (Materials Chemistry) at Stockholm University, Senior Scientist at DuPont, CTO at Biofiber Tech Sweden, R&amp;D Intern at Max Planck Institute for Polymer Research</p><p><strong>Connect on:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/luis-v-717aab8a\">LinkedIn</a> or <a href=\"mailto:luis@greewave.com\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"https://rubra-q.com/\">Greewave</a> develops bio-based rubber alternatives from European forestry and citrus waste, producing drop-in latex materials that integrate with existing rubber manufacturing infrastructure to reduce dependency on imported natural rubber and petroleum-based synthetics.</p><p><strong>HQ:</strong> Sweden</p><p><strong>Industry:</strong> CleanTech, Advanced Materials | <strong>Team Size:</strong> 3</p><div><hr></div><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share Company Launch Tracker&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\"><span>Share Company Launch Tracker</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p>Stay strapped in,</p><p>Drake</p><div><hr></div><p><em>Thanks for reading. If you enjoyed this, share it with your friends, colleagues, and anyone who wants to stay ahead of the latest startup launches and emerging companies in tech.</em></p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://companylaunchtracker.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&q